name: Kristin Manna
bio: Kristin is one of six kids. Her dad likes to get married. She drinks orange juice with everything. She is a horrible speller. Kristin has performed at Eastville Comedy Club, Gotham Comedy Club, Greenwich Village Comedy Club, UCBEast, and various clubs in NYC. Kristin has been featured in the She Devil Woman's Comedy Festival. She also produces and writes her web series " Awkwardly Charming". Most recently, you may have seen Kristin eating pancakes in an IHOP commercial.
